\s NDAGOMBA GUSA NAWE
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Ndagomba gusa nawe, nse nawe mu mutima; ndagomba gusa nawe. We wakunda gusenga; kenshi wiherereye, Mwami mpa gusa nawe.\bd*
\pc \bdit Nta jambo ribi Mwami bumvis’\bdit*\bdit  \bdit*\bdit uvuga ntiwigeze utongana wavuga neza; ndagomba gusa nawe wew’\bdit*\bdit  Ugororotse \bdit*\bdit Mwami mpa gusa nawe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ndagomba gusa nawe wew’\bd*\bd  Ugororotse \bd*\bd wihanganiy’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd ababi, nyigiza hafi yawe Mwami mpa wa mutima ngo nse nawe vy’ukuri\bd*\bd .\bd*
\pc \bdit Nta jambo ribi Mwami bumvis’ uvuga ntiwigeze utongana wavuga neza; ndagomba gusa nawe wew’ Ugororotse Mwami mpa gusa nawe.\bdit*
\zoli1 \bd Ndagomba gusa nawe nah’\bd*\bd  \bd*\bd abantu bakwanka bakugirira nabi; \bd*\bd Wewe \bd*\bd ntiwabihoye mbere warabakunda \bd*\bd Wabagirira \bd*\bd neza.\bd*
